415d72de_1172x781.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:781,&quot;width&quot;:1172,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:712,&quot;bytes&quot;:373261,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:false,&quot;topImage&quot;:true,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7d52818b-ef3c-425a-ac6e-0bbe415d72de_1172x781.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7d52818b-ef3c-425a-ac6e-0bbe415d72de_1172x781.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7d52818b-ef3c-425a-ac6e-0bbe415d72de_1172x781.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7d52818b-ef3c-425a-ac6e-0bbe415d72de_1172x781.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" fetchpriority="high"></picture></div></a> <polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line><figcaption class="image-caption"> <a href="https://unsplash.com/@michael97?utm_content=creditCopyText&amp;utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_source=unsplash">Zhanhui li</a>的照片在<a href="https://unsplash.com/photos/brown-concrete-building-1iuxWsIZ6ko?utm_content=creditCopyText&amp;utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_source=unsplash">Unsplash</a>上</figcaption></figure></div><p>您可能认为这将是关于大学校长最近对校园内反犹太主义<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5VtAZBvmzcQ">的灾难性证词</a>的争议，以及一直<a href="https://twitter.com/BillAckman/status/1734401275142291640">试图使他们开除的</a>大捐助者的灾难性证词。好吧，很抱歉让您失望，但这并不是真正的 - 或至少仅是切线。我承认，反犹太主义的争吵让我想到了这个话题，但精英大学捐款的问题已经在我脑海中盘旋了一段时间。</p><p>实际上，几十年了。我去了一所精英大学（斯坦福大学），我们总是被提醒捐款对该机构有多么重要。校友、基金会和其他个人的捐赠为大学捐赠基金提供了资金，而捐赠基金的回报是巨大的现金来源。 2019年，<a href="https://www.thecrimson.com/article/2019/4/19/harvard-revenue-half-donors/">哈佛大学的首席财务官声称</a>该学校的年收入中有45％归因于当前或过去的捐款。查看<a href="https://sr.ithaka.org/publications/an-overview-of-state-higher-education-funding-approaches/">国家统计数据</a>表明，哈佛并不是太多的异常值。在非营利4年的大学中，大约三分之一的收入来自礼物或捐赠回报。 </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fdd664018-b6fa-41a4-908a-7f89d65ab1f9_868x702.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fdd664018-b6fa-41a4-908a-7f89d65ab1f9_868x702.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fdd664018-b6fa-41a4-908a-7f89d65ab1f9_868x702.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fdd664018-b6fa-41a4-908a-7f89d65ab1f9_868x702.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fdd664018-b6fa-41a4-908a-7f89d65ab1f9_868x702.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsub