75466360">支持</a>，欧洲公司通过将投资从中国移出，意大利从腰带和道路项目中<a href="https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-06/italy-notified-china-it-will-exit-belt-and-road-pact-radiocor">撤出</a>来“ <a href="https://www.reuters.com/world/with-eye-china-eu-maps-out-de-risking-economic-security-strategies-2023-10-05/">降低风险</a>”，等等。但是，汽车行业引起了很多关注的痛点。</p><p>基本上，中国正在用电动汽车淹没欧洲。在过去的两年中，中国已经从汽车行业的一个也是世界上最大的汽车出口国。电动汽车是这些出口中的很大一部分，中国大部分电动汽车销售都用于欧洲： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fdf3ef51d-3917-4c8b-8031-a78f43164947_827x480.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fdf3ef51d-3917-4c8b-8031-a78f43164947_827x480.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fdf3ef51d-3917-4c8b-8031-a78f43164947_827x480.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fdf3ef51d-3917-4c8b-8031-a78f43164947_827x480.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fdf3ef51d-3917-4c8b-8031-a78f43164947_827x480.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fdf3ef51d-3917-4c8b-8031-a78f43164947_827x480.jpeg" width="706" height="409.770253929867" data-attrs="{&