n class="image-caption">资料来源：国际清洁运输委员会</figcaption></figure></div><p>但是中国的电动汽车出口激增是最近的，所以让我们介绍一下它发生的一些原因。</p><p>首先，这是<a href="https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-09-14/from-cheap-money-to-tax-breaks-evs-in-china-get-a-lot-of-love?sref=R8NfLgwS">一篇关于中国EV补贴政权的好文章</a>。中国向制造商支付一项价值超过1400美元的补贴，他们为电动汽车公司提供廉价的土地和融资，并在该行业中大力补贴研发。中国和欧洲都向人们付款以购买电动汽车，其政府直接购买电动汽车。但是，中国比欧洲补贴的地方要多得多。</p><p>这是中国出口优势的原因之一，但不是唯一的出口。另一个是中国<a href="https://www.bloomberg.com/graphics/2023-breaking-china-ev-supply-chain-dominance/?sref=R8NfLgwS">几乎控制电动电池的整个供应链</a>，除了最初的采矿外： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F9a475e8d-8036-4778-a0eb-54378b3d35af_812x672.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F9a475e8d-8036-4778-a0eb-54378b3d35af_812x672.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F9a475e8d-8036-4778-a0eb-54378b3d35af_812x672.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F9a475e8d-8036-4778-a0eb-54378b3d35af_812x672.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F9a475e8d-8036-4778-a0eb-54378b3d35af_812x672.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F9a475e8d-8036-4778-a0eb-54378b3d35af_812x672.jpeg" width="642" height="531.3103448275862" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/9a475e8d-8036-4778-a0eb-54378b3d35af_812x672.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:672,&quot;width&quot;:812,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:642,&quot;bytes&quot;:130880,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F9a475e8d-8036-4778-a0eb-54378b3d35af_812x672.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F9a475e8d-8036-4778-a0eb-54378b3d35af_812x672.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F9a475e8d-8036-4778-a0eb-54378b3d35af_812x672.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F9a475e8d-8036-4778-a0eb-54378b3d35af_812x672.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div><figcaption class="image-caption">资料来源： <a href="https://www.bloomberg.com/graphics/2023-breaking-china-ev-supply-chain-dominance/?sref=R8NfLgwS">彭博社</a></figcaption></figure></div><p>电动汽车比内燃机要简单得多，这基本上只是带车轮的电池。电动汽车中的电池约占汽车购买价格的<a href="https://www.bloomberg.com/graphics/2023-breaking-china-ev-supply-chain-dominance/?sref=R8NfLgwS">40％</a> 。当供应商在NextDoor上，大量发电机会容易得多。 <a href="https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2023-09-28/eu-needs-more-than-just-tariffs-to-counter-china-s-electric-cars?sref=R8NfLgwS">欧洲的电池比中国贵33％</a> 。</p><p>电池也约为电动汽车<em>重量</em>的四分之一。他们在中国制造的一切都减少了您可以通过在消费者附近找到汽车工厂可以节省的运输成本。</p><p>另一个原因是宏观经济。众所周知，中国正处于<a href="https://www.cnbc.com/2023/12/09/inflation-in-china-november-consumer-prices-fall-fastest-in-3-years.html">经济放缓的巨大放缓</a>之中，尽管所有消费补贴都减少了对新电动汽车的需求。欧洲的经济也处于垃圾场，但中国基本计划为中国经济生产足够的电动汽车，而中国的经济比最终的经济更快。因此，中国电动汽车生产商<a href="https://www.bloomberg.com/features/2023-china-ev-graveyards/?sref=R8NfLgwS">陷入了大量库存</a>，他们不能在国内销售。因此，他们正在削减价格并将库存倾倒在欧洲。</p><p>最后，让我们不要打折中国汽车，电池工程师和企业家的创造力和创新。该行业向电动汽车的转变赋予了新贵的汽车制造商，这是一个世纪以来的一次机会，可以在旧线公司的根深蒂固的统治地位上进行最终奔跑，这些公司知道内燃机的内燃机工程。欧洲初创公司<em>可能</em>会挑战大众汽车，雷诺和梅赛德斯·奔驰。他们没有。取而代之的是像Byd和Saic这样的中国公司，以及一家美国公司特斯拉（Tesla）抓住了这一天。</p><p>因此，由于补贴，供应链的优势，技术转变以及宏观经济学，欧洲将大量的廉价中国电动汽车倾倒在其市场上。欧洲的领导人对此感到生气， <a href="https://www.technologyreview.com/2023/09/26/1080293/europe-chinese-ev-investigation-subsidy/">呼吁调查</a>中国电动汽车补贴。这可能<a href="https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-09-13/europe-is-provoking-china-with-its-probe-into-electric-car-aid?sref=R8NfLgwS">以对中国制造的汽车的关税结束</a>。在最近的中国欧盟峰会之后的<a href="https://apnews.com/article/china-eu-summit-divide-europe-b11a0c31182257fbca67a6fd16a2fe72">新闻发布会</a>上，欧洲委员会主席乌苏拉·冯·莱恩说：</p><blockquote><p>如果您只看过去两年，那么贸易赤字就翻了一番。对于许多欧洲人来说，这是一个非常关心的问题……根本原因是众所周知的，我们讨论了它们……在政治上，欧洲领导人将无法容忍我们的工业基础受到不公平竞争的破坏……公平起见。</p></blockquote><p> （我应该提到的是，欧洲不是唯一的思考。土耳其也在使用非宣传障碍物来<a href="https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-09/turkey-moves-to-counter-rising-tide-of-chinese-ev-imports?sref=R8NfLgwS">阻止中国制造的电动汽车</a>淹没该国。）</p><p>鉴于汽车行业对欧洲经济的重要性，这种反应并不令人惊讶。在一个电子制造业聚集在亚洲和软件聚集在美国的世界中，汽车制造是欧洲仍然<a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/List_of_countries_by_motor_vehicle_production#/media/File:Motor_Vehicle_Prod_volume_RITA_T1-23.svg">相对强大的</a>主要领域。这是一个成熟的行业，因此欧洲对<a href="https://apnews.com/article/ai-act-europe-regulation-59466a4d8fd3597b04542ef25831322c">新技术进行调节的</a>恋物癖不太可能损坏它。这是一个重型工业，因此，集聚的力量不如电子设备强大，在那里零件可以便宜地运输；汽车生产往往在世界范围内分布，大多数汽车都在售出的地方生产，这使欧洲能够制造大部分汽车，即使其经济总体上失去了竞争力和动力。尤其是德国拥有繁荣的汽车工程才能，使他们能够制造出非常好的汽车（或者至少是非常好的<em>内燃烧</em>车）。</p><p>因此，失去汽车行业可能会沿着去工业化的道路进一步推动欧洲。廉价中国电动汽车是<a href="https://apnews.com/article/electric-vehicles-china-subsidies-europe-investigation-4f00df1c7588ca375efebb89a2b83783">欧洲消费者的福音</a>，它们有助于加快绿色过渡并减少碳排放。但是，竞争也有可能使一群欧洲工人退出工作，<a href="https://www.acea.auto/figure/employment-in-eu-automotive-sector/">这是该地区在汽车行业工作的7％</a> 。传统上，欧洲比美国更关心保护其行业免受外国竞争的影响。与中国的电动汽车争吵是对是否仍然如此的测试，或者欧洲是否接受了更多的“新自由主义”贸易方法。</p><p>但是这里也可能有一个国家安全角度。乌克兰战争被僵化了，即使美国国内政治在危险中对乌克兰的支持也使美国对乌克兰的支持也是如此。这意味着支持乌克兰持续独立的工作将落到欧洲。而且，如果乌克兰确实跌倒，欧洲仍然会陷入困境，因为普京将把目光转向波兰和波罗的海。因此，欧洲将需要在诸如炮弹，导弹，炮兵，防空，无人机和装甲车等地区与俄罗斯战争制作相匹配。国内汽车行业使欧洲在需要时可以更大的能力重新利用生产线并在需要时提高国防生产。如果汽车产业逃往中国，欧洲将更容易受到俄罗斯的影响。实际上，这是汽车行业今天在全球分布的原因之一。第二次世界大战期间和之后，许多国家都认为，为了维持强大的军队，他们需要汽车行业。</p><p>因此，如果欧洲确实决定保护其汽车行业，它将做什么？当然，对中国制造的汽车的关税是一种选择，但它们具有几个明显的限制。首先，它们的影响将受到汇率调整的限制；人民币将简单地反对欧元贬值，至少部分抵消了关税。同样，关税对帮助欧洲汽车制造商在以前占主导地位的出口市场中变得更有竞争力。事实是，中国制造的电动汽车几乎比目前欧洲制造的电动汽车<em>要好</em>，而且关税不会改变这一点。</p><p>为了解决这些问题，欧洲需要的不仅仅是关税。它需要等同于《美国降低通货膨胀法》，这是一项主要的生产补贴计划，不仅是为电动汽车本身，而且对于电池和矿产加工设施而言。欧洲还需要简化和削减过去几年中汽车行业堆积的一些<a href="https://www.euronews.com/business/2023/12/07/why-europes-evs-are-years-behind-china-despite-250bn-investment">监管的过度生长</a>。而且它需要更严重地在EV部门进行研发。</p><p>另一个重要的一步是欧洲最近避开了近期的事情：鼓励初创企业。初创企业制造商特斯拉（Tesla）能够在通用汽车和福特的老巨人周围运行戒指，这并不巧合，并非常依赖遗产市场和传统技术。欧洲没有特斯拉；如果它确实想与中国竞争，它至少需要一个。</p><p>换句话说，如果欧洲要拯救其汽车行业，那么在过去的几十年中，它将不得不终于留下舒适的停滞。受监管和自满的驱动，这种停滞从来都不是真正可持续的。一旦像汽车制造这样的旧tentpole行业受到外部冲击的打击，整个系统就会不可避免地吱吱作响和崩溃。</p><p>欧洲很长时间以来一直很幸运 - 内燃机保持了主导地位，中国的需求饥饿地摇动了德国制造的汽车。但是震惊以向电动汽车的转变形式出现，现在漫长而轻松的白日梦结束了。 Europe&#39;s leaders can choose to meet the challenge, or they can hold more meetings and issue more empty rhetoric. Incidentally, that&#39;s the same choice that&#39;s facing them on a great many fronts right now. </p><div><hr></div><p class="button-wrapper" data-attrs="{&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.noahpinion.blog/subscribe?&quot;,&quot;text&quot;:&quot;Subscribe now&quot;,&quot;action&quot;:null,&quot;class&quot;:null}" data-component-name="ButtonCreateButton"><a class="button primary" href="https://www.noahpinion.blog/subscribe?"><span>现在订阅</span></a></p><p class="button-wrapper" data-attrs="{&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/car-wars?utm_source=substack&utm_medium=email&utm_content=share&action=share&quot;,&quot;text&quot;:&quot;Share&quot;,&quot;action&quot;:null,&quot;class&quot;:null}" data-component-name="ButtonCreateButton"> <a class="button primary" href="https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/car-wars?utm_source=substack&utm_medium=email&utm_content=share&action=share"><span>分享</span></a></p>; 
Why are your groceries still so expensive? A deep dive into a mysterious and troubling question. https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/why-are-your-groceries-still-so-expensive https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/why-are-your-groceries-still-so-expensiveNoah Smith Fri, 08 Dec 2023 08:06:00 GMT <div class="captioned-image-container"><figure> <a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fb5f37920-8dbc-41eb-93ca-9132e1536e3c_1022x680.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fb5f37920-8dbc-41eb-93ca-9132e1536e3c_1022x680.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fb5f37920-8dbc-41eb-93ca-9132e1536e3c_1022x680.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fb5f37920-8dbc-41eb-93ca-9132e1536e3c_1022x680.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fb5f37920-8dbc-41eb-93ca-9132e1536e3c_1022x680.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fb5f37920-8dbc-41eb-93ca-9132e1536e3c_1022x680.jpeg" width="1022" height="680" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/b5f37920-8dbc-41eb-93ca-9132e1536e3c_1022x680.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:680,&quot;width&quot;:1022,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:325454,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:false,&quot;topImage&quot;:true,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fb5f37920-8dbc-41eb-93ca-9132e1536e3c_1022x680.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fb5f37920-8dbc-41eb-93ca-9132e1536e3c_1022x680.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fb5f37920-8dbc-41eb-93ca-9132e1536e3c_1022x680.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fb5f37920-8dbc-41eb-93ca-9132e1536e3c_1022x680.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" fetchpriority="high"></picture></div></a> <polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line><figcaption class="image-caption"> Photo by <a href="https://unsplash.com/@jediahowen?utm_content=creditCopyText&amp;utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_source=unsplash">Jed Owen</a> on <a href="https://unsplash.com/photos/bread-on-white-ceramic-plate-beside-sliced-bread-on-table-q6Y8Xr3SoQA?utm_content=creditCopyText&amp;utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_source=unsplash">Unsplash</a></figcaption></figure></div><p> The big economic debate right now is over why consumer sentiment is still very low. Although negative narratives — “vibes” — may <a href="https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/vibes-vs-data">play a part</a> , economic numbers like inflation surely matter a lot. In <a href="https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/at-least-five-interesting-things-bff">my roundup</a> this week, I flagged <a href="https://www.briefingbook.info/p/digesting-inflation">some evidence</a> showing that it takes people a while to get over the negative psychic impact of high inflation, even after a temporary burst of inflation is over. It seems likely that if prices go back down to where they used to be, it would help people feel better faster.</p><p> For some products, this actually happens. Gasoline prices have fallen by over a third since mid-2022, and are lower than they were a decade ago in dollar terms: </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7ff08f9b-bf72-4d17-abec-06dd8a48788a_1318x450.png" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7ff08f9b-bf72-4d17-abec-06dd8a48788a_1318x450.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7ff08f9b-bf72-4d17-abec-06dd8a48788a_1318x450.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7ff08f9b-bf72-4d17-abec-06dd8a48788a_1318x450.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.